description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 2, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 2, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Leverage for East, Nine Lives for South, and 8 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70021-36984-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [2 Votes, Common]
